003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Coponia\">Coponia\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Am\n                    emta\">Am-\u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[em]ta\u003C/span>\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-text=\"vixit\">v(ixit)\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-text=\"annis\">an(nis)\u003C/span> · L · \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"dis\">D\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"manibus\">M\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Coponia Am\n                    emta\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Coponia\">COPONIA\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Am\n                    emta\">AM\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[..]TA\u003C/span>\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-text=\"vixit\">V\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-text=\"annis\">AN\u003C/span>·L·\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000157_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-05.\" src=\"ISic000157_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000157.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-05.\" src=\"ISic000157-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000157_rear_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-05.\" src=\"ISic000157_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000157_rear.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-05.\" src=\"ISic000157_rear-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text on basis of autopsy\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-8417-7089\">Tuuli Ahlholm\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>To the Shades of the Underworld. Coponia Amemta lived 50 years.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Ferrua suggests that the full restoration of the missing cognomen from lines 2-3 is Amemta, which is of Greek origin, and which is rare, but is more commonly found in the masculine form (Amemptos), deriving from the adjective commonly found in contemporary Greek funerary inscriptions in Sicily. There are two other attestations of members of the gens Coponia from Thermae Himeraeae, see \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000156\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000156\u003C/a> and \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000158\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000158\u003C/a>, and another attestation from Messana, see \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000273\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000273\u003C/a>. As Bivona (1994) stresses, the gens Coponia is represented by a handful of republican senators and one equestrian procurator of Judaea under Augustus.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 1994.0777 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 1977.0339 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 78 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1941 262 no.22 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002655\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002655\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[229,232,235,238,241,244],{"id":230,"html":231},"editions","\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"dis\">d(is)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"manibus\">m(anibus)\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Coponia Am\n                    emta\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Coponia\">Coponia\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Am\n                    emta\">Am-\u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[em]ta\u003C/span>\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-text=\