photo J. Prag 2023-07-05.\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"rear\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic000157_rear_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-05.\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000157_rear.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-05.\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n        \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#TA #AA\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\" xml:id=\"APΤAK\"/>\u003Cw xml:id=\"APΤAU\">\u003Cexpan xml:id=\"APΤAe\">\u003Cabbr xml:id=\"APΤAo\">d\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex xml:id=\"APΤAy\">is\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/w> \u003Cw xml:id=\"APΤAΙ\">\u003Cexpan xml:id=\"APΤAΤ\">\u003Cabbr xml:id=\"APΤAε\">m\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex xml:id=\"APΤAο\">anibus\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/w> \n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\" xml:id=\"APΤBA\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\" xml:id=\"APΤBK\">\u003Cname xml:id=\"APΤBU\">Coponia\u003C/name> \u003Cname xml:id=\"APΤBe\">Am\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\" break=\"no\" xml:id=\"APΤBo\"/>\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\" xml:id=\"APΤBy\">em\u003C/supplied>ta\u003C/name>\u003C/persName> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\" xml:id=\"APΤBΙ\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cw xml:id=\"APΤBΤ\">\u003Cexpan xml:id=\"APΤBε\">\u003Cabbr xml:id=\"APΤBο\">v\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex xml:id=\"APΤCA\">ixit\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/w> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\" xml:id=\"APΤCK\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cw xml:id=\"APΤCU\">\u003Cexpan xml:id=\"APΤCe\">\u003Cabbr xml:id=\"APΤCo\">an\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex xml:id=\"APΤCy\">nis\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/w> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\" xml:id=\"APΤCΙ\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cnum value=\"50\" xml:id=\"APΤCΤ\">L\u003C/num> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\" xml:id=\"APΤCε\">·\u003C/g>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text on basis of autopsy\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#TA\">\n                \u003Cp>To the Shades of the Underworld. Coponia Amemta lived 50 years.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\" resp=\"#AA\">\n                \u003Cp>Ferrua suggests that the full restoration of the missing cognomen from lines 2-3 is Amemta, which is of Greek origin, and which is rare, but is more commonly found in the masculine form (Amemptos), deriving from the adjective commonly found in contemporary Greek funerary inscriptions in Sicily. There are two other attestations of members of the gens Coponia from Thermae Himeraeae, see \u003Cref target=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000156\">ISic000156\u003C/ref> and \u003Cref target=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000158\">ISic000158\u003C/ref>, and another attestation from Messana, see \u003Cref target=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000273\">ISic000273\u003C/ref>. As Bivona (1994) stresses, the gens Coponia is represented by a handful of republican senators and one equestrian procurator of Judaea under Augustus.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"AE\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>1994.0777\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/R46KDTZX\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"AE\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>1977.0339\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/R46KDTZX\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"ILMusTermini\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>78\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/JCV85C79\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Ferrua\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1941\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>262 no.22\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/P7QQ9SB6\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002655\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002655\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
